From 111936e66b93abba492ce96cfcd989a864a09833 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ramanathan Choodamani <rchoodam@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 16 Jul 2025 12:01:47 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:DP:wifi:ath12k:Add support to use fse metadata in rx
 path

Use the fse metadata tag to decide if UL packet can be delivered
directly to PPE

For every flow entered into the FST table, a metadata will be
populated for that flow. Using this tag, decide if the packet
can directly go to the PPE driver if the ppe_vp_num is valid

Pkg upgrade notes:
Original patch: 999-QSDK-DP-wifi-ath12k-add-support-to-include-fast-rx-i.patch

Patch-dependency: 0132-0002-QSDK-wifi-ath12k-Add-helper-functions-for-calculatin.patch
Patch-work: NA
Tag: FSE

Signed-off-by: Ramanathan Choodamani <rchoodam@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/core.h              |    1 
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/fse.h               |    3 
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hal.h               |    4 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_rx.c       |   64 +++++++++++++++++---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal.h         |    9 ++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal_qcn9274.c |    1 
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal_qcn9274.h |   19 +++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal_rx_desc.h |   10 ++-
